reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Candles are included!
reviews.reviewText: First off, the 2 candles in the ad are actually included with these candle holders, which is awesome. I wasn’t aware of that, so I had already purchased other candles. The included candles are nice, are battery operated, and good quality. The fake candle flame flickers when they are on. It’s an actual fake plastic flame that wiggles when turned on, and a light shines on it from inside the candle. It looks very realistic. However, the plastic flame tends to make a clicking noise when it wiggles back and forth, unless you adjust it and make sure it is centered on the wire that it hangs from.On to the candle holders themselves. They are wonderful! They are high quality and sturdy. I would buy these again in a heartbeat!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Beautiful lanterns!! Bought these for my outdoor decor for Christmas. The candle isn’t attached ti the lantern and kept blowing around I moved them inside and decided I liked them better inside lol my cats are obsessed with them the wick moves like a real flame. Very pretty and affordable thinking of buying more!!

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Look cute , very lightweight
reviews.reviewText: These look pretty nice but they are not sturdy or heavy, very lightweight metal but they worked well for me for staging our house.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I placed these on my fireplace hearth and they are quite charming looking. I'm not too sure how long the "wicks" are going to last. They seem a bit flimsy but they aren't necessary so if they happen to break off it won't be a big problem.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Small price for big impact
reviews.reviewText: These lamps and candles are awesome! The glow that they give is very realistic and flickers. There is a little noise that they make when the wick is flickering. They are easy to turn on and turn off. They are also very impactful.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Makes clicking sounds that kind of sound like a fireplace haha.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Not for outdoor use as described
reviews.reviewText: The lanterns are basic but appropriate for outdoor use. The round handles do not stay up as the pictures show. The candles that cone with then cannot be used in an uncovered outdoor area. They worked great at first but once they were exposed to moisture, they no longer worked.
